Comedy of Power;;45;;82;;NC;;In this comedy-drama from Claude Chabrol, Magistrate Jeanne Charmant-Killman (Isabelle Huppert) doggedly investigates CEO Michel Humeau (François Berléand), who is accused of participating in massive corporate malfeasance. As her investigation leads her into the upper echelons of government, Jeanne becomes intoxicated by the power she is amassing. Though she faces threats by those whom she would see brought low and by the dissolution of her personal life and marriage, she will not relent.;;Drama,Comedy;;Claude Chabrol;;2006;;Isabelle Huppert,François Berléand,Patrick Bruel,Robin Renucci,Marilyne Canto,Thomas Chabrol,Jean-François Balmer,Pierre Vernier,Jacques Boudet,Philippe Duclos,Roger Dumas,Yves Verhoeven;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/comedy_of_power